<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section class="faq-section" data-aos="fade-up">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p class="text-center mb-5">Quick answers to common questions about visiting or contacting Creamy Bar</p>

        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <div class="faq-item active">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <span>What are your COVID-19 safety measures?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>We follow all local health guidelines and have implemented enhanced cleaning protocols. Our staff wears masks and gloves, and we offer contactless payment options. We also have spacing markers for lines and limited indoor seating capacity.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <span>Do you offer catering for events?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes! We offer full-service catering for all types of events from birthday parties to corporate functions. We provide ice cream carts, sundae bars, and customized flavor options. Contact us with your event details for a personalized quote.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <span>How can I apply for a job at Creamy Bar?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>We're always looking for enthusiastic team members! You can apply in person at any of our locations or send your resume to careers@creamybar.com. We typically hire for seasonal positions in spring and permanent positions year-round.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <span>Do you have dairy-free or vegan options?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Absolutely! We offer a rotating selection of dairy-free flavors made with coconut milk, almond milk, or oat milk. We also have vegan options that contain no animal products. Check our flavor board or ask our staff for the current offerings.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <div class="faq-question">
                        <span>Can I order custom ice cream cakes?</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes, we create custom ice cream cakes for any occasion! We need at least 48 hours notice for custom cakes. You can choose from our available flavors and design options. Visit our store or call us to place a custom cake order.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

